tags.name: LT 28 Traffic Cameras/LT-56 Traffic Camera LHS panel

testSteps.description: Given I am at the LiveTraffic Website
When I click on the menu button
And I click "Traffic Cameras" button from the menu list

Then I should see list of Camera regions from All Cameras tab
| Camera_Region |
| Inner Sydney |
| Sydney North |
| Sydney West |
| Sydney South |
| Regional North |
| Regional South |
| All Regional |
| All NSW |
| All Sydney |
When I click "Sydney West" button from All Cameras List
Then I should Camera Region name "Sydney West" on page

Then I should see list of below cameras from "Sydney West" region
| Camera_Locations |
| Church Street (Parramatta) |
| Cumberland Highway (Merrylands) |
| James Ruse Drive (Rosehill) |
| M4 Western Motorway (Minchinbury) |
| M4 Western Motorway (Prospect) |
| M4 Western Motorway (St Marys) |
| M7 (Glenwood) |
| M7 at The Horsley Drive (Horsley Park) |
| Old Windsor Road (Beaumont Hills) |
| Old Windsor Road (Winston Hills) |
| Parramatta Road (Parramatta) |
| Seven Hills Road (Seven Hills) |
| M4 Western Motorway (Auburn) |
| Great Western Highway (Hazelbrook) |
| M4 Western Motorway (Mays Hill) |
| Silverwater Road (Silverwater) |
